Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: The Minorca Condominium is an 8-story building built in 2005 with the top-5 floors consisting of residential units. Building amenities are available to commercial businesses and include a recreation room, exercise room, infinity pool, yoga lawn and out door terrace with manicured landscaping.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Amenities include conference room, fitness center, full bank service, deli and car wash service
With a WalkScore® of 99 out of 100, there are many amenities including banks, restaurants, and hotels within walking distance
